actionConfiguration.body:
select   top.id ,top.objectives_task , top.objectives_results ,top.objectives_quarter , to2.objectives_naem ,top.estimate_time, top.results_assessment, top.objectives_status from   t_objectives_personal top  
left join  t_objectives to2  on top.objectives_id = to2.id 
where top.objectives_type = 2
and top.objectives_quarter = {{Select1.selectedOptionValue}} and top.create_by = {{appsmith.user.name}}
